title: Daniel Tosh Standup - Mont Bleu, Lake Tahoe - Dec 21 2013
description:
Daniel throws out some new funny stuff, enjoy! Photography was strictly prohibited... 
While his body language does compliment his jokes, it's still very enjoyable.

This was a video on YT with 100K+ views that was recently taken down by Daniel Tosh c/o Ziffren Brittenham LLP.
This is unacceptable... So please, download and enjoy!

...And don't forget to SEED!
